title: Thin Lizzy - Philo In Philadelphia - Live Philadelphia 77 (by Fr
description:
Thin Lizzy - Philo In Philadelphia - Live October 1977

Hi!

This is THIN LIZZY. This a live Show from October 26th 1977. Some songs were "polished up" and used for the famous Live and Dangerous CD. The sound is great, it is a soundboard recording. The versions of Dancing In The Moonlight or Warrior are awesome. There are   also songs like Johnny which was rarely played. Great songs, great audience talk from Phil Lynott.
The show with the best sound. I have a lot of recordings, this is the best! Better than the official ones!
